notesStmt.note: Title from p. iii, with attribution "elargita a D. Sebastiano Perto"[in a second hand] from p. i.

msContents.summary: Begins with Rubrica statutoru novoru ... (detailed table of contents), [p. iii-xii], ends with a month-by-month list of local feast days and movable feasts, p. 218-222.

supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i (contemporary paper) + 135; [xxviii], 1-222, [223-242]; contemporary pagination in ink, modern pagination in pencil, upper outer corner.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by one hand.

origin.p: Written in Italy in the late 16th or early 17th century (Zacour-Hirsch).
